author: Screen Junkies
description:
It's the Honest Trailer for The Electric State! The film with a budget larger than the GDP of a small nation is here to raise the price on your Netflix subscription! It's got robots, Chris Pratt, and Millie Bobby Brown thrown together in the way only an algorithm could enjoy. Welcome to the future! It sucks here!
